Images of our fleet on the ground are a powerful reminder of the severity of this crisis. At any given time, at least 52 of 61 aircraft in our jet fleet can be seen resting on HNL’s tarmac, waiting for the moment they can reconnect Hawai‘i to the world. https://t.co/fsoPAsOSig https://t.co/OuEZzCGa82

We're excited to share the stories of three members from our @HawaiianAir ʻohana as they prepare for the most prestigious hula competition of its kind: the Merrie Monarch Festival.
